---
name: "approval-prompt-dialog"
version: "1.0.0"
layer: "extension"
description: "Generic approval dialog shown before a pipeline stage requiring user confirmation"
params:
  - name: "stageName"
    type: "string"
    description: "Pipeline stage name requesting approval"
    required: true
  - name: "issueNumber"
    type: "number"
    description: "Issue number being processed"
    required: true
  - name: "summary"
    type: "string"
    description: "Short summary of what will happen if approved"
    required: true
  - name: "planFile"
    type: "string"
    description: "Path to the plan file (if applicable)"
    required: false
---
**{{stageName}}** — Issue #{{issueNumber}}

{{summary}}
{{#if planFile}}
Plan: `{{planFile}}`
{{/if}}

Approve to continue, or cancel to stop the pipeline.
